    "Notably, our survey focuses on learning tasks with communication in multi-agent deep reinforcement learning, including the intersection with emergent language.",
    "4 Within this focus, multiple agents often operate in partially observable environments and learn to share information encoded through neural networks.l+1 = l + ∇ J() ∇ 𝜃 i J 𝜃 i = ⃗ o,⃗ a∼D ∇ 𝜃 i 𝜇 i a i | o i ∇ a i Q 𝜇 i ⃗ o, a 1, …, a N | a i =𝜇 i (oi)Furthermore, communication protocols, determining when and with whom to communicate, often leverage deep learning models to find the optimal choices that minimize communication overhead and yield more targeted communication.",
    "A multitude of works have been proposed to handle these subproblems inherent in Comm-MADRL.",
    "Most research works model only one or a few aspects of Comm-MADRL while selecting a default approach for other aspects.",
    "Given that the common goal of Comm-MADRL approaches is to design an effective and efficient communication protocol to improve agents' learning performance in the environment, the proposed Comm-MADRL approaches inevitably share similarities to some extent."
